{"tid":1841114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本上 如果奶左武漢肺炎 你本身已經係一件生化武器","createTime":"2020-01-25T06:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T09:27:50.000Z","uid":13663,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e2454efa6ddf36d6044dbadb07c5f2c337bc10","tid":1841114,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"香港人 報仇！"},{"pid":"2881f285c09bc16b77750b06be3de856a25db6d9","tid":1841114,"uid":13663,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8e9F3W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8e9F3W.jpg&h=6e03c086&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0cd93b8c6856495c313e06aba71ca2c0fdd3c39","tid":1841114,"uid":267408,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"咳嗽師要Up Level!！<br />\n<br />\n雖然而家越來越多人帶口罩，藍屍癈佬越黎越容易辨認出黎。<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日，你隨時已被WARS 感染！萬一你已受感染，你甘心默默消失？<br />\n<br />\n根據最新既統計，老人家最容易受感染，而衣個族羣正正係最多支持中共港共既人！<br />\n<br />\n最重要係將D唔戴口罩既癈佬蝗蟲感染！衣幾日仲要係癈老聯宜既高峰期！！<br />\n<br />\n將衣堆威脅人類將來係立會選舉之前全數消滅！！<br />\n<br />\n咳嗽師！開年啦！！<br />\n<br />\n（Sor9y 1999)"},{"pid":"a77197a32246dde8d7e6150ebfe6b89066fdde21","tid":1841114,"uid":282777,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c9a933c9b626d98edf2444cbdd547aa5b52d742","tid":1841114,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92ed751902253e195e3c949d8dedd902b86d27c","tid":1841114,"uid":221342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f318c6273594770f9519d41f7bc59b7959b7add6","tid":1841114,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"禮崩虎<img src=